
[1]bolting

   BOLTING,ppr. Fastening with a bolt, or bolts; blurting out; shooting
   forth suddenly; separating bran from flour; sifting; examining;
   discussing; dislodging.

   BOLTING, n. The act of fastening with a bolt or bolts; a sifting;
   discussion.
